                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COMPACT DESIGN: Hook and clip nest together when not in use. SIZE MINI gate clearance 1.1\", hook clearance 1.5\", dimensions when open 1.8\" x 4.6\".",
